{"word":"G2923 - κριτής - kritḗs - kree-tace' - Judge","slug":"G2923","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κριτής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kritḗs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kree-tace'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Judge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>κριτής</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Krites</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>kree-tace'</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> one who passes or arrogates to himself, judgment on anything </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> an arbiter </p> <p class='li520'><b>b.</b> of a Roman procurator administering justice </p> <p class='li520'><b>c.</b> of God passing judgment on men </p> <p class='li520'><b>d.</b> of the leaders or rulers of the Israelites </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 18:42,5 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Noun Masculine <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>; a <i>judge</i> (generally or specifically): - judge. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}